<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p3.6">Here <math alttext="\xi^{\mu}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p3.6.m1.1"><semantics id="S2.p3.6.m1.1a"><msup id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.2" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.2.cmml">ξ</mi><mi id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.3" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.3.cmml">μ</mi></msup><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p3.6.m1.1b"><apply id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1">superscript</csymbol><ci id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.2">𝜉</ci><ci id="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.3.cmml" xref="S2.p3.6.m1.1.1.3">𝜇</ci></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p3.6.m1.1c">\xi^{\mu}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p3.6.m1.1d">italic_ξ start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT italic_μ end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> is the general timelike Killing vector that fulfills in the Killing equation <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib92" title="">Wald:1984rg </a></cite>,</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E7">
