<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p3.7">Also, the Killing vector is related to the Ricci tensor <math alttext="R_{\mu}^{\nu}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1"><semantics id="S2.p3.7.m1.1a"><msubsup id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.2" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.2.cmml">R</mi><mi id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.3" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.3.cmml">μ</mi><mi id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.3" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.3.cmml">ν</mi></msubsup><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1b"><apply id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1">superscript</csymbol><apply id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.1.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.2.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.2">𝑅</ci><ci id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.3.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.2.3">𝜇</ci></apply><ci id="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.3.cmml" xref="S2.p3.7.m1.1.1.3">𝜈</ci></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1c">R_{\mu}^{\nu}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p3.7.m1.1d">italic_R start_POSTSUBSCRIPT italic_μ end_POSTSUBSCRIPT start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT italic_ν end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> via the following relation <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib92" title="">Wald:1984rg </a></cite></p>
