</div>
<div class="ltx_para" id="S2.p4">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p4.5">Following the approach of <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib78" title="">Sheykhi:2012vf </a></cite>, we can obtain the following relation for the total mass enclosed by the holographic screen</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E9">
<tbody><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
