</tr></tbody>
</table>
<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p12.3">This is the second Friedmann equation in the setup of modified entropic cosmology (MEC). This equation is in agreement with the result of <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib79" title="">Sheykhi:2011sqb </a></cite>, in which the modified Friedmann equations were derived from considering the temperature corrections in Newton’s laws. It is important to note that in our result the general function <math alttext="f(\ddot{a})" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p12.2.m1.1"><semantics id="S2.p12.2.m1.1a"><mrow id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.cmml"><mi id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.2" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.2.cmml">f</mi><mo id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.1" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mrow id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.3.2" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.cmml"><mo id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.3.2.1" stretchy="false" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.cmml">(</mo><mover accent="true" id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.2" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.2.cmml">a</mi><mo id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.1" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.1.cmml">¨</mo></mover><mo id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.3.2.2" stretchy="false" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.cmml">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p12.2.m1.1b"><apply id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2"><times id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.1.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.1"></times><ci id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.2.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.2">𝑓</ci><apply id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.2.3.2"><ci id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.1">¨</ci><ci id="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p12.2.m1.1.1.2">𝑎</ci></apply></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p12.2.m1.1c">f(\ddot{a})</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p12.2.m1.1d">italic_f ( over¨ start_ARG italic_a end_ARG )</annotation></semantics></math> replaces the Debye function <math alttext="\mathcal{D}(x)" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p12.3.m2.1"><semantics id="S2.p12.3.m2.1a"><mrow id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.cmml"><mi class="ltx_font_mathcaligraphic" id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.2" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.2.cmml">𝒟</mi><mo id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.1" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mrow id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.3.2" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.cmml"><mo id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.3.2.1" stretchy="false" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.cmml">(</mo><mi id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.1" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.1.cmml">x</mi><mo id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.3.2.2" stretchy="false" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.cmml">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p12.3.m2.1b"><apply id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2"><times id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.1.cmml" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.1"></times><ci id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.2.cmml" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.2.2">𝒟</ci><ci id="S2.p12.3.m2.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p12.3.m2.1.1">𝑥</ci></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p12.3.m2.1c">\mathcal{D}(x)</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p12.3.m2.1d">caligraphic_D ( italic_x )</annotation></semantics></math>, which was used as the temperature correction function in the analysis of <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib79" title="">Sheykhi:2011sqb </a></cite>.</p>
</div>
<div class="ltx_para" id="S2.p13">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p13.1">From the component “<math alttext="rr" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p13.1.m1.1"><semantics id="S2.p13.1.m1.1a"><mrow id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.2" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml">r</mi><mo id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.1" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mi id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.3" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml">r</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p13.1.m1.1b"><apply id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1"><times id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.1"></times><ci id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.2">𝑟</ci><ci id="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml" xref="S2.p13.1.m1.1.1.3">𝑟</ci></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p13.1.m1.1c">rr</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p13.1.m1.1d">italic_r italic_r</annotation></semantics></math>” of the modified Einstein equation (<a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#S2.E12" title="In II Modified Entropy Gravity ‣ Cosmological Implications of Modified Entropic Gravity"><span class="ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">12</span></a>), we arrive at the following result</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E35">
<tbody><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_align_center"><math alttext="f(\ddot{a})\left(a\ddot{a}+2\dot{a}^{2}+2k\right)+4\pi Ga^{2}\left(p-\rho%
\right)=0\,." class="ltx_Math" display="block" id="S2.E35.m1.2"><semantics id="S2.E35.m1.2a"><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.cmml"><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.cmml"><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.2.cmml"><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.3" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.3.cmml">f</mi><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.2.cmml">⁢</mo><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.4.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.cmml"><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.4.2.1" stretchy="false" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.cmml">(</mo><mover accent="true" id="S2.E35.m1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S2.E35.m1.1.1.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.2.cmml">a</mi><mo id="S2.E35.m1.1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.1.cmml">¨</mo></mover><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.4.2.2" stretchy="false" xref="S2.E35.m1.1.1.cmml">)</mo></mrow><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.2a" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.2.cmml">⁢</mo><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.cmml"><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.cmml">(</mo><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.cmml"><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.cmml"><mi id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.2.cmml">a</mi><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mover accent="true" id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3.cmml"><mi id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3.2" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3.2.cmml">a</mi><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.2.3.1.cmml">¨</mo></mover></mrow><mo id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.1" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.cmml">+</mo><mrow id="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.3" xref="S2.E35.m1.2.2.1.1.1.1.1.1.1.3.cmml"><mn id="S2.E35.m1.2.