<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p13.2">By combining this equation with Eq. (<a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#S2.E34" title="In II Modified Entropy Gravity ‣ Cosmological Implications of Modified Entropic Gravity"><span class="ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">34</span></a>), we acquire the first Friedmann equation in the MEC model as</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E36">
<tbody><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
