<div class="ltx_para" id="S2.p15">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p15.2">From the continuity equations for the individual components of the Universe, the variations of the energy densities with a scale factor are obtained as follows</p>
<table class="ltx_equationgroup ltx_eqn_align ltx_eqn_table" id="S5.EGx4">
<tbody id="S2.E39"><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
