<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p15.1">For each component “<math alttext="i" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p15.1.m1.1"><semantics id="S2.p15.1.m1.1a"><mi id="S2.p15.1.m1.1.1" xref="S2.p15.1.m1.1.1.cmml">i</mi><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S2.p15.1.m1.1b"><ci id="S2.p15.1.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S2.p15.1.m1.1.1">𝑖</ci></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S2.p15.1.m1.1c">i</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S2.p15.1.m1.1d">italic_i</annotation></semantics></math>” of matter-energy content, the normalized density parameter in our scenario is defined as</p>
