<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p15.3">The sum of the normalized energy densities is unity,</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E43">
<tbody><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
