<div class="ltx_para" id="S2.p16">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p16.2">For comparing the results of our cosmology model with the observational data, it is much better to use the conventional density parameter instead of the normalized density parameter. The conventional density parameter is defined as</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E44">
