<p class="ltx_p" id="S2.p16.3">It is important to note that, in contrast to the sum of the normalized density parameters, the sum of the conventional density parameters in our scenario is opposite to unity and instead is equal to</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S2.E45">
