</div>
<div class="ltx_para" id="S3.SS2.p3">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S3.SS2.p3.1">In this study, we use the BAO dataset from 6dF <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib89" title="">Beutler:2011hx </a></cite>, SDSS <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib90" title="">SDSS:2009ocz </a></cite>, and WiggleZ <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib91" title="">Blake:2011wn </a></cite> measurements. These data are presented in Table <a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#S3.T1" title="Table 1 ‣ III.2 BAO Data ‣ III Observational Data ‣ Cosmological Implications of Modified Entropic Gravity"><span class="ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">1</span></a>. The <math alttext="\chi^{2}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1"><semantics id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1a"><msup id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.2" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml">χ</mi><mn id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.3" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml">2</mn></msup><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1b"><apply id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1">superscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.2">𝜒</ci><cn id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1.1.3">2</cn></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1c">\chi^{2}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS2.p3.1.m1.1d">italic_χ start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT 2 end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> for this dataset is computed by using</p>
<table class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table" id="S3.E58">
<tbody><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_align_center"><math alttext="\chi_{BAO}^{2}=\underset{i,j}{\sum}\left(\left.d_{z}\left(z_{i}\right)\right|_%
{\mathrm{th}}-\left.d_{z}\left(z_{i}\right)\right|_{\mathrm{obs}}\right)C_{ij}%
