="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS2.p3.2.m1.1d">italic_C start_POSTSUBSCRIPT italic_i italic_j end_POSTSUBSCRIPT start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT - 1 end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> is the inverse of the covariance matrix and it is given by <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib91" title="">Blake:2011wn </a></cite></p>
