_{m0}}H_{0}\left(1+z_{*}\right)D_{A}(z_{*})\,.</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.E60.m1.1d">italic_R ( italic_z start_POSTSUBSCRIPT ∗ end_POSTSUBSCRIPT ) = divide start_ARG 1 end_ARG start_ARG italic_c end_ARG square-root start_ARG roman_Ω start_POSTSUBSCRIPT italic_m 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT end_ARG italic_H start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT ( 1 + italic_z start_POSTSUBSCRIPT ∗ end_POSTSUBSCRIPT ) italic_D start_POSTSUBSCRIPT italic_A end_POSTSUBSCRIPT ( italic_z start_POSTSUBSCRIPT ∗ end_POSTSUBSCRIPT ) .</annotation></semantics></math></td>
