<section class="ltx_subsection" id="S3.SS4">
<h3 class="ltx_title ltx_title_subsection">
<span class="ltx_tag ltx_tag_subsection">III.4 </span>The SH0ES <math alttext="H_{0}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1"><semantics id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1b"><msub id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.2" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml">H</mi><mn id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.3" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml">0</mn></msub><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1c"><apply id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.2">𝐻</ci><cn id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.1.m1.1.1.3">0</cn></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1d">H_{0}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS4.1.m1.1e">italic_H start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> Measurement</h3>
<div class="ltx_para" id="S3.SS4.p1">
<p class="ltx_p" id="S3.SS4.p1.3">Finally, we include the SH0ES team’s <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib9" title="">Riess:2021jrx </a></cite> measurement of the Hubble constant <math alttext="H_{0}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1"><semantics id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1a"><msub id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml">H</mi><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml">0</mn></msub><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1b"><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.2">𝐻</ci><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.3.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1.1.3">0</cn></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1c">H_{0}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS4.p1.1.m1.1d">italic_H start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math>, which quantifies the current expansion rate of the Universe. The Hubble constant is usually expressed as <math alttext="H_{0}=100h\,\mathrm{km\ s^{-1}Mpc^{-1}}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1"><semantics id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1a"><mrow id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.cmml"><msub id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.2.cmml">H</mi><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.3.cmml">0</mn></msub><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.1" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.1.cmml">=</mo><mrow id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.cmml"><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.cmml">100</mn><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.3.cmml">h</mi><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1a" lspace="0.170em" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1.cmml">⁢</mo><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.4" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.4.cmml">km</mi><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1b" lspace="0.500em" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1.cmml">⁢</mo><msup id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.2" mathvariant="normal" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.2.cmml">s</mi><mrow id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.cmml"><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3a" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.cmml">−</mo><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.2.cmml">1</mn></mrow></msup><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1c" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1.cmml">⁢</mo><msup id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.2.cmml">Mpc</mi><mrow id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.cmml"><mo id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3a" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.cmml">−</mo><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.2.cmml">1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1b"><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1"><eq id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.1"></eq><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.2">𝐻</ci><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.3.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.2.3">0</cn></apply><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3"><times id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.1"></times><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2">100</cn><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.3.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.3">ℎ</ci><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.4.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.4">km</ci><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5">superscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.2">s</ci><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3"><minus id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3"></minus><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.2.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.5.3.2">1</cn></apply></apply><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6">superscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.2">Mpc</ci><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3"><minus id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3"></minus><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.2.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.6.3.2">1</cn></apply></apply></apply></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1c">H_{0}=100h\,\mathrm{km\ s^{-1}Mpc^{-1}}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS4.p1.2.m2.1d">italic_H start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT = 100 italic_h roman_km roman_s start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT - 1 end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT roman_Mpc start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT - 1 end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math>. In the SH0ES project <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib9" title="">Riess:2021jrx </a></cite>, the value of <math alttext="H_{0}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1"><semantics id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1a"><msub id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.cmml"><mi id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.2" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.2.cmml">H</mi><mn id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.3" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.3.cmml">0</mn></msub><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content" id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1b"><apply id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.1.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.2.cmml" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.2">𝐻</ci><cn id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.3.cmml" type="integer" xref="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1.1.3">0</cn></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1c">H_{0}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S3.SS4.p1.3.m3.1d">italic_H start_POSTSUBSCRIPT 0 end_POSTSUBSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math> is determined by using observations of Cepheid variable stars and Type Ia supernovae as standard candles to establish precise distances to galaxies. By comparing these distances with the galaxies’ redshifts, they derive a direct measurement of the Hubble constant. The inferred value from this project is <cite class="ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite"><a class="ltx_ref" href="https://arxiv.org/html/2503.08236v1#bib.bib9" title="">Riess:2021jrx </a></cite></p>
