" xref="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2"><csymbol cd="ambiguous" id="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2.1.cmml" xref="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2">subscript</csymbol><ci id="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2.2.cmml" xref="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2.2">ℒ</ci><ci id="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2.3.cmml" xref="S4.p1.2.m2.1.1.3.2.3.2.3">tot</ci></apply></apply></apply></apply></apply></annotation-xml><annotation encoding="application/x-tex" id="S4.p1.2.m2.1c">\chi_{{\rm tot}}^{2}=-2\ln\mathcal{L}_{\mathrm{tot}}</annotation><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun" id="S4.p1.2.m2.1d">italic_χ start_POSTSUBSCRIPT roman_tot end_POSTSUBSCRIPT start_POSTSUPERSCRIPT 2 end_POSTSUPERSCRIPT = - 2 roman_ln caligraphic_L start_POSTSUBSCRIPT roman_tot end_POSTSUBSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math>. Thus, we have</p>
